  eventmachine-0.12.10-r2.ebuild, +files/eventmachine-0.12.10-gentoo.patch:
  Add a patch to fix a few more problems in eventmachine, such as bug
  #317281.

*eventmachine-0.12.10-r2 (19 Apr 2010)

